title: D.C. nightclub shooting leaves 5 injured
content:
D.C. police are looking for a person involved in a nightclub shooting early Saturday morning that injured five people.
Police said a man went into the DC Soundstage and began shooting at about 2:30 a.m. Saturday. He injured one woman and four men -- all of whom suffered non-life threatening injuries.
There are no suspects as of Saturday afternoon, D.C. police said, and a motive is unknown.
